Menagerie
=========

Menagerie is a multi-class World of Warcraft (The Burning Crusade) rotation addon.

It is a fork of, and derives directly from, the original **Flux AIO** TBC rotation
codebase. The rotation logic, architecture (the Strategy Registry pattern, the
per-class module layout, the TMW profile build pipeline), and substantial portions
of the source were created by the Flux AIO author(s). Menagerie rebrands that work —
renaming the project, its Lua namespace, and its hosting — but the foundation belongs
to the upstream project.

Original project: Flux AIO
Upstream URL:     https://github.com/flux-rotations/tbc
Author(s):        the Flux AIO project (flux-rotations)

Grateful acknowledgement to the Flux AIO author(s) for the original work this fork
is built upon.

